  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240°C/ 220°C (fan)/ gas 9</p><p>Put a large baking tray in the oven to heat up (this will stop the pizza bottoms from going soggy!)</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step1-new-x200.png",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step1-new-x400.png",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step1-new-x700.png",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step1-new-x1000.png",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step1-new-x1500.png",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>lighter cheese</strong> and<strong> Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella </strong>into rough bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step2-new-x200.png",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step2-new-x400.png",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step2-new-x700.png",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step2-new-x1000.png",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step2-new-x1500.png",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> dried oregano </strong>and <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a small bowl with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[4 tbsp]</span><strong> cold water</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>,<strong> sugar </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix to combine – this is your<strong> tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> pizza bases</strong> to the heated baking tray, divide and spoon the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> over them evenly</p><p>Top with the <strong>grated lighter cheese</strong>,<strong> Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until the cheese is bubbling and starting to brown – these are your <strong>triple cheese pizzas</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step4-new-x200.png",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step4-new-x400.png",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/983.-step4-new-x700.png",
